Okay, it's time to peel some things!

00:03:07.673 --> 00:03:11.068
We all know that carrots
are good for us, yes?

00:03:11.395 --> 00:03:13.634
The better to see you with.

00:03:15.335 --> 00:03:17.538
You could do about a cup of these.

00:03:18.554 --> 00:03:20.529
I spotted these fresh green beans,

00:03:20.529 --> 00:03:22.813
kind of a garden veggie soup today.

00:03:24.339 --> 00:03:26.055
So I'm going to wash these guys,

00:03:26.055 --> 00:03:28.760
I'm also just going to
take two stalks of celery

00:03:28.760 --> 00:03:32.090
with me to the sink to do a quick bath.

00:03:34.431 --> 00:03:36.333
Now it's time to put the carrots in

00:03:36.333 --> 00:03:38.039
because these take a
little bit longer to cook,

00:03:38.039 --> 00:03:41.160
