00:04:12.265 --> 00:04:13.564
one, it's fun,

00:04:13.564 --> 00:04:17.176
but two, I can have a
better handle on my corn.

00:04:18.071 --> 00:04:19.620
Oh! (laughs)

00:04:19.620 --> 00:04:20.984
See, just like that,

00:04:20.984 --> 00:04:22.758
