00:04:33.842 --> 00:04:36.847
Then I'm going to pop in the corn.

00:04:37.093 --> 00:04:39.633
There's something about
working with fresh ingredients.

00:04:40.553 --> 00:04:42.595
I'm just going to take the
green beans and the celery

00:04:42.595 --> 00:04:44.556
and throw them into the pot.

00:04:46.807 --> 00:04:51.169
We continue by adding a
little vegetable broth.

00:04:51.751 --> 00:04:53.955
And by a little I mean a lot (laughs).

00:04:55.790 --> 00:04:58.297
Starting to look really yummy in here.

00:04:59.414 --> 00:05:02.072
And now it's time for

00:05:02.072 --> 00:05:05.100
