00:05:05.160 --> 00:05:07.378
Just going to take it off the stem.

00:05:07.378 --> 00:05:08.759
Like so.

00:05:08.759 --> 00:05:10.779
I add the leafy greens because

00:05:10.779 --> 00:05:12.880
I like the texture of it in the soup

00:05:12.880 --> 00:05:15.987
and I also want the extra nutrients.

00:05:15.987 --> 00:05:18.836
Just thinning it a bit
so that, when you eat it,

00:05:18.836 --> 00:05:22.990
